com.interpss.core.algo.mslf

Interface BaseMultiStateLfAlgorithm<TNet extends AclfNetwork>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, NetworkRef<TNet>, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    MultiNetDclfAlgorithm<TNet>, MultiStateAclfAlgorithm<TNet>, MultiStateDclfAlgorithm<TNet>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseMultiStateLfAlgorithmImpl, MultiNetDclfAlgorithmImpl, MultiStateAclfAlgorithmImpl, MultiStateDclfAlgorithmImpl

    public interface BaseMultiStateLfAlgorithm<TNet extends AclfNetwork>
extends NetworkRef<TNet>
    A representation of the model object 'FS Loadflow Algorithm'. Base class for defining a multiple state algorithm object. It contains a basecase AclfNetwork object, a set of cloned AclfNetwork objects.

    The following features are supported:

    • One Net2 Multi Lf Algo
    • Fixed Structure
    • NOf Lf Algoritms
    • Ms Aclf Net List
    See Also:
    MslfAlgorithmPackage.getBaseMultiStateLfAlgorithm()
